        </div>
        <div id="section-content">
            <p class="text-size--small">
                <b>
                    The Bridges Community Trust is dedicated to serving the Meadows and Clifton communities and
                    surrounding areas, to provide better local services and facilities.
                </b>
            </p>

            <p class="text-size--small">
                We have a long established working relationship with the local community and local VCS organisations.
                Primarily, we deliver employment services, which contribute to the local community by raising the
                standards of living, giving locals more disposable income, and contributing to the health and wellbeing
                of the local residents.
            </p>
